arStrings.szText: {c_important}Razor Wings{/c} makes enemies {c_important}{u}Vulnerable{/u}{/c} for {c_number}{SF_15}{/c} seconds when hitting with a Critical Strike or from behind.
{c_important}Razor Wings{/c} has a {c_number}[{SF_16} * 100|%|]{/c} chance to regain a Charge when hitting an enemy. Double this chance if you have an active {c_important}{u}Barrier{/u}{/c}.
{c_important}Razor Wings{/c} last {c_number}[{SF_28}*100|%|]{/c} longer and spiral outwards.
